Class MultiFilePBEventStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.slac.archiverappliance.PlainPB.MultiFilePBEventStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Iterable<Event>, EventStream, RemotableOverRaw

    public class MultiFilePBEventStream
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventStream, RemotableOverRaw
    An eventstream that spans multiple PB files. You can only get one iterator out of this event stream. This condition is also checked for. This is typically used with/after PlainPBFileNameUtility.getFilesWithData

    mshankar
